    "content": "<p><img class=\"wscnph\" src=\"//img30.360buyimg.com/venderrule//jfs/t1/265390/6/21362/274505/67b45c86Fedc48991/5e8df4df6ae4c61e.png\" width=\"900\" /></p>\n<p>【规则原文】</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">1</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、《京东开放平台招商资质标准细则》</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\"><a style=\"color: #0563c1; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=2614\">https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=2614</a></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">2</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、《京东开放平台&ldquo;0元开店&rdquo;试运营管理规则》</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\"><a style=\"color: #0563c1; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=915123374395625472\">https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=915123374395625472</a></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">3</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、《京东开放平台盲盒商品管理规则》</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\"><a style=\"color: #0563c1; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=833317602301448192\">https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=833317602301448192</a></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\